{"tid":1512761,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"中共唔明白 其實港獨最大推手係刁帝","createTime":"2019-08-28T04:28:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-28T04:46:25.000Z","uid":36134,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"75b9b59a65356fc696430fadd5d4cb92ed63a00f","tid":1512761,"uid":36134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T04:28:13.000Z","msg":"係自由社會越壓迫越會反抗<br />\n真係催生 滋養港獨個個人就係<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">刁帝</span></span><br />\n<br />\n佢上台一改過往對香港既懷柔政策<br />\n全面滲透同控制香港 壓迫香港人既政治空間<br />\n要求香港人只係要做國際既賺錢機器 <br />\n輸錢輸血比中共<br />\n中共呢幾年對香港係 <br />\n又要權又要錢又要人<br />\n貪得無厭<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n結果終於搞出大獲<br />\n刁帝而家仲要繼續強硬鎮壓<br />\n結果只會適得其反<br />\n只會將更多香港人推向港獨陣營"},{"pid":"e7b98ef1a3414b8a65440dc9b90e4bda1728e07b","tid":1512761,"uid":38494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T04:28:51.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">8.28 停止國泰白色恐怖 愛丁堡廣場</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">8.28 #Metoo 遮打花園</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">8.31 民陣遊行 直指中聯辦</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">9.01 機場 13:00</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">9.02 全港三罷</div><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">今晚見</div></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">光復香港 時代革命</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">五大訴求 缺一不可</div></span>"},{"pid":"d21dda3